title: Softmax only taking one arguement
body_html: Per pytorch documentation (http://pytorch.org/docs/master/nn.html#torch-nn-functional) the softmax function should be able to take dimension as an input. However, I'm getting this error: TypeError: softmax() takes exactly 1 argument (2 given).
